<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.132.37009.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Swertia hongquanii A seedlings showing basal leaves B root C flowering plant D flower showing corolla, nectaries, stamens and pistil E capsule F seeds. Drawn by Jing Tian." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/340833" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.132.37009.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Habitat and morphology of Swertia hongquanii. A-B Habitat C flowering plant D seedlings showing basal leaves E adaxial view of flower showing calyx, corolla, nectaries, stamens and pistil F abaxial view of flower showing calyx and corolla G stem with a pair of leaves H flowering and fruiting plant; centrally, a capsule with persistent corolla can be seen. Photos: Jiaxiang Li." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/340834" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.132.37009.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Seeds of Swertia hongquanii. Scale bars: 1 mm (A); 0.5 mm (B); 0.2 mm (C); 0.3 mm (D-F). Photos: Jiaxiang Li." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/340835" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

